Class ActiveBoxGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.geom.RectangularShape
      • java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D

              • edu.xtec.jclic.boxes.ActiveBoxBag
                • edu.xtec.jclic.boxes.ActiveBoxGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resizable, Shape, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class ActiveBoxGrid
extends ActiveBoxBag
implements Cloneable
    This class is a ActiveBoxBag with constructors that take an argument of type Shaper to build all its ActiveBox elements. It also mantains info about the number of "rows" and "columns", useful to compute appropiate (integer) values when resizing the ActiveBoxBag and its ActiveBox children.
    Version:
    13.08.28
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
